{"tid":671751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人可以而家出嚟聽我呻","createTime":"2018-05-20T11:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T13:07:12.000Z","uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b404cc8de789032cdf575b8092f3ece62db073c0","tid":671751,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"近排同返啲好耐無見嘅朋友食飯<br />\n佢地都搵到自己熱衷嘅事<br />\n有人讀電影 有人做free lance畫家 有人讀翻譯<br />\n反觀返自己 混混噩噩<br />\n無興趣亦無專長 淨係識得用錢嚟衡量<br />\n我ex問過我 我一起身想做啲咩 我做咩會開心 我鍾意食咩<br />\n我一樣都答唔到<br />\n咁多年人生都好似空白一片咁<br />\n我真係好撚迷惘 失敗 一事無成<br />\n<br />\n擺低個tg希望有好心人俾個出口我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/numbndumb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnumbndumb&d=oKrDNViBTcHj%2FpYdazgxp%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=60999c41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/numbndumb</a><br />\n利申 天水圍"},{"pid":"6d6325daaaaf914a356944c63d2b08cc6ab6c84d","tid":671751,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐在係屋企樓下喊<br />\n其實我唔敢俾朋友知我咁垃圾<br />\n佢地個個都以為我志向堅定"},{"pid":"62bb6351c3e727dcce4214ea16d469f62c9b66fa","tid":671751,"uid":4351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"嚟屯門我搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef4d9936e2593dabb9a5478223cbf4a1e33e22e","tid":671751,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62bb6351c3e727dcce4214ea16d469f62c9b66fa","tid":671751,"uid":4351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"嚟屯門我搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:45:36.000Z","msg":"喊住搭車好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屯門邊到"},{"pid":"aa8b63b3d3e17eed27c6f733c1541ed6c04ce91e","tid":671751,"uid":4351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2